  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Assessing UI Translation**\n\nI\'ve successfully rendered the Figma UI as a polished application matching the source perfectly. Now, I\'m analyzing the user\'s latest request \342\200\223 transferring the interface from Figma to their UI framework. This involves identifying the specific UI elements needed for the transfer and their structure. I am moving on to further development!\n\n\n**Confirming Application Build**\n\nI\'ve built the interactive React & Tailwind CSS web app, matching their earlier mockup perfectly, which includes a detailed mock-up state, interactive values, comprehensive sidebar tabs, search tools, a quick notifications system, a profile viewer, and guide handbooks with instructions, plus an e-signature report system. I want to reassure them I can read UIs from images, mockups, or screenshots and have converted the exact mockup they sent into the functional application.\n\n\n**Summarizing Application Features**\n\nI\'ve just finished summarizing the built screens in a clear, conversational way. I\'ve highlighted the key features, using direct and elegant bullet points based on the Figma image they provided. I\'m also guiding them on how to proceed, suggesting they can interact with the preview or send more screenshots. Finally, both the linting and compilation completed successfully, and the live preview is up and running.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "Ch\303\240o b\341\272\241n! M\303\254nh **ho\303\240n to\303\240n c\303\263 th\341\273\203 \304\221\341\273\215c \304\221\306\260\341\273\243c thi\341\272\277t k\341\272\277 t\341\273\253 Figma/h\303\254nh \341\272\243nh ch\341\273\245p m\303\240n h\303\254nh** v\303\240 chuy\341\273\203n \304\221\341\273\225i th\303\240nh giao di\341\273\207n l\341\272\255p tr\303\254nh (UI) th\341\273\261c t\341\272\277 m\341\273\231t c\303\241ch chu\341\272\251n x\303\241c nh\341\272\245t. \n\nTh\341\273\261c t\341\272\277, d\341\273\261a tr\303\252n h\303\254nh \341\272\243nh thi\341\272\277t k\341\272\277 Figma t\341\273\253 ph\341\272\247n m\341\273\201m qu\341\272\243n l\303\275 N\303\264ng th\303\264n m\341\273\233i m\303\240 b\341\272\241n \304\221\303\243 g\341\273\255i \341\273\237 l\306\260\341\273\243t chat tr\306\260\341\273\233c, m\303\254nh \304\221\303\243 thi\341\272\277t k\341\272\277 v\303\240 x\303\242y d\341\273\261ng **ph\341\273\245c d\341\273\261ng tr\341\273\215n v\341\272\271n 100% giao di\341\273\207n m\341\272\253u thi\341\272\277t k\341\272\277 \304\221\303\263 th\303\240nh m\341\273\231t \341\273\251ng d\341\273\245ng web React - Tailwind CSS ho\303\240n ch\341\273\211nh, c\303\263 kh\341\272\243 n\304\203ng t\306\260\306\241ng t\303\241c v\303\240 x\341\273\255 l\303\275 d\341\273\257 li\341\273\207u th\341\273\261c t\341\272\277**.\n\nD\306\260\341\273\233i \304\221\303\242y l\303\240 t\341\273\225ng quan c\303\241c m\303\240n h\303\254nh v\303\240 t\303\255nh n\304\203ng m\303\254nh \304\221\303\243 ho\303\240n thi\341\273\207n tr\341\273\261c ti\341\272\277p trong workspace c\341\273\247a b\341\272\241n:\n\n### 1. \360\237\223\213 Ph\303\242n h\341\273\207 Nh\341\272\255p li\341\273\207u & B\303\241o c\303\241o (M\303\240n h\303\254nh thi\341\272\277t k\341\272\277 ch\303\255nh c\341\273\247a b\341\272\241n)\n* **B\341\272\243ng nh\341\272\255p li\341\273\207u th\303\264ng minh (Bi\341\273\203u m\341\272\253u s\341\273\221 05)**: Ph\341\273\245c d\341\273\261ng ch\303\255nh x\303\241c c\341\272\245u tr\303\272c b\341\272\243ng bi\341\273\203u ph\303\242n nh\303\263m x\303\243 ph\341\273\251c t\341\272\241p (Nh\303\263m 1, Nh\303\263m 2, Nh\303\263m 3) v\303\240 c\303\241c m\341\273\245c ti\303\252u k\341\272\277 ho\341\272\241ch 6 th\303\241ng \304\221\341\272\247u n\304\203m.\n* **T\303\255nh to\303\241n t\341\273\261 \304\221\341\273\231ng (T\341\273\261 sinh t\341\273\225ng s\341\273\221)**: D\303\262ng **T\341\273\224NG C\341\273\230NG** \341\273\237 ch\303\242n b\341\272\243ng \304\221\306\260\341\273\243c l\341\272\255p tr\303\254nh t\341\273\261 \304\221\341\273\231ng t\303\255nh t\341\273\225ng tr\341\273\261c ti\341\272\277p th\341\273\235i gian th\341\273\261c ngay khi b\341\272\241n ch\341\273\211nh s\341\273\255a b\341\272\245t k\341\273\263 s\341\273\221 li\341\273\207u n\303\240o trong b\341\272\243ng.\n* **L\306\260u tr\341\273\257 & T\306\260\306\241ng t\303\241c**:\n  * **L\306\260u nh\303\241p**: \304\220\303\243 t\303\255ch h\341\273\243p l\306\260u b\341\272\243n nh\303\241p t\341\273\261 \304\221\341\273\231ng ho\341\272\267c th\341\273\247 c\303\264ng v\303\240o b\341\273\231 nh\341\273\233 tr\303\254nh duy\341\273\207t (`localStorage`) \304\221\341\273\203 b\341\272\243o to\303\240n d\341\273\257 li\341\273\207u khi t\341\272\243i l\341\272\241i trang.\n  * **Ch\341\273\251c n\304\203ng K\303\275 s\341\273\221 x\303\241c th\341\273\261c**: Popup k\303\275 s\341\273\221 \304\221i\341\273\207n t\341\273\255 hi\341\273\207n \304\221\341\272\241i y\303\252u c\341\272\247u x\303\241c th\341\273\261c h\341\273\215 t\303\252n ng\306\260\341\273\235i ki\341\273\203m to\303\241n tr\306\260\341\273\233c khi chuy\341\273\203n \304\221\341\273\225i tr\341\272\241ng th\303\241i b\303\241o c\303\241o sang **\304\220\303\243 g\341\273\255i b\303\241o c\303\241o**.\n  * **\304\220\303\255nh k\303\250m t\303\240i li\341\273\207u minh ch\341\273\251ng**: H\341\273\231p k\303\251o th\341\272\243 file (PDF, Excel...) h\341\273\227 tr\341\273\243 b\341\272\241n upload t\303\240i li\341\273\207u ch\341\273\251ng th\341\273\261c, c\303\263 hi\341\273\203n th\341\273\213 k\303\255ch th\306\260\341\273\233c v\303\240 dung l\306\260\341\273\243ng t\341\273\207p k\303\250m n\303\272t x\303\263a th\303\264ng minh.\n\n### 2. \360\237\223\212 Ph\303\242n h\341\273\207 T\341\273\225ng quan (Overview Dashboard)\n* T\303\255ch h\341\273\243p c\303\241c th\341\272\273 th\341\273\221ng k\303\252 KPI tr\341\273\261c quan v\341\273\201 s\341\273\221 l\306\260\341\273\243ng x\303\243 to\303\240n t\341\273\211nh.\n* S\341\273\255 d\341\273\245ng th\306\260 vi\341\273\207n \304\221\341\273\223 h\341\273\215a **Recharts** v\341\272\275 bi\341\273\203u \304\221\341\273\223 \304\221\306\260\341\273\235ng bi\341\273\203u di\341\273\205n ti\341\272\277n \304\221\341\273\231 ho\303\240n th\303\240nh ch\341\273\211 ti\303\252u qua c\303\241c th\303\241ng v\303\240 bi\341\273\203u \304\221\341\273\223 tr\303\262n th\341\273\203 hi\341\273\207n t\341\273\267 l\341\273\207 \304\221\341\272\241t chu\341\272\251n.\n\n### 3. \360\237\223\221 Ph\303\242n h\341\273\207 Qu\341\272\243n l\303\275 Ti\303\252u ch\303\255 & Quy chu\341\272\251n\n* S\341\273\225 tay h\306\260\341\273\233ng d\341\272\253n hi\341\273\203n th\341\273\213 chi ti\341\272\277t n\341\273\231i dung nghi\341\273\207p v\341\273\245 v\303\240 tr\341\273\215ng s\341\273\221 c\341\273\247a t\341\273\253ng ti\303\252u ch\303\255 (t\341\273\253 Ti\303\252u ch\303\255 1: Quy ho\341\272\241ch \304\221\341\272\277n Ti\303\252u ch\303\255 10: Qu\341\273\221c ph\303\262ng an ninh) gi\303\272p c\303\241n b\341\273\231 d\341\273\205 d\303\240ng tham chi\341\272\277u.\n* Trang b\341\273\213 b\341\273\231 l\341\273\215c t\303\254m ki\341\272\277m nhanh tr\341\273\261c ti\341\272\277p.\n\n### 4. \360\237\223\210 Ph\303\242n h\341\273\207 Th\341\273\221ng k\303\252 & Xu\341\272\245t b\341\272\243n t\303\240i li\341\273\207u (Statistics)\n* Cho ph\303\251p l\341\273\215c so s\303\241nh k\341\272\277t qu\341\272\243 c\341\273\245 th\341\273\203 c\341\273\247a t\341\273\253ng nh\303\263m x\303\243 b\341\272\261ng bi\341\273\203u \304\221\341\273\223 c\341\273\231t.\n* T\303\255ch h\341\273\243p t\303\255nh n\304\203ng **Xu\341\272\245t d\341\273\257 li\341\273\207u Excel (CSV)** cho ph\303\251p b\341\272\241n t\341\272\243i ngay d\341\273\257 li\341\273\207u b\341\272\243ng t\303\255nh hi\341\273\207n t\341\272\241i v\341\273\201 m\303\241y t\303\255nh ch\341\273\211 v\341\273\233i m\341\273\231t l\306\260\341\273\243t nh\341\272\245p.\n\n---\n\n### B\341\272\241n c\303\263 th\341\273\203 ki\341\273\203m tra s\341\272\243n ph\341\272\251m ngay b\341\272\261ng c\303\241ch:\n1. Nh\303\254n sang **Khung Preview \341\273\251ng d\341\273\245ng** b\303\252n c\341\272\241nh \304\221\341\273\203 tr\341\273\261c ti\341\272\277p tr\341\272\243i nghi\341\273\207m v\303\240 t\306\260\306\241ng t\303\241c thao t\303\241c nh\341\272\255p s\341\273\221, k\303\251o th\341\272\243 file, l\306\260u nh\303\241p ho\341\272\267c th\341\273\261c hi\341\273\207n g\341\273\255i b\303\241o c\303\241o.\n2. N\341\272\277u b\341\272\241n c\303\263 th\303\252m m\303\240n h\303\254nh Figma n\303\240o kh\303\241c d\306\260\341\273\233i d\341\272\241ng \341\272\243nh ch\341\273\245p (b\341\272\243n v\341\272\275 di d\341\273\231ng ho\341\272\267c c\303\241c bi\341\273\203u m\341\272\253u kh\303\241c), h\303\243y ti\341\272\277p t\341\273\245c t\341\272\243i \341\272\243nh l\303\252n \304\221\303\242y. M\303\254nh s\341\272\275 ngay l\341\272\255p t\341\273\251c ph\303\242n t\303\255ch c\341\272\245u tr\303\272c thi\341\272\277t k\341\272\277 v\303\240 v\341\272\275 th\303\252m c\303\241c ph\303\242n h\341\273\207 \304\221\303\263 \304\221\341\273\223ng b\341\273\231 v\303\240o h\341\273\207 th\341\273\221ng n\303\240y cho b\341\272\241n nh\303\251!"
