  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Grasping the User\'s Query**\n\nI\'m focused on understanding the user\'s core concern: maintaining synchronization between their Figma designs and this application, specifically avoiding issues with potentially \"out of sync\" data transfers. My priority is to fully grasp their apprehension about the workflow, so I can devise the best response.\n\n\n**Defining Collaboration Process**\n\nI\'m now formulating the optimal collaboration strategy. I\'m considering the best way we can work together: I understand both visual cues from images and detailed descriptions from Figma links. My strength lies in interpreting layouts and components directly from images shared in the chat. My goal is to develop a synchronized, cohesive app, so I\'m devising methods to reassure the user about this.\n\n\n**Clarifying Synchronization Methods**\n\nI am now outlining a clear, step-by-step collaborative process. I\'m focusing on user input: the user can provide a complete Figma overview image (depicting multiple screens/user flows), or numbered screenshots alongside a Figma link for detailed implementation. I will suggest developing an all-in-one state, structuring the React code with shared state to ensure the best performance.\n\n\n**Refining Feedback Loop**\n\nI\'m now iterating on the feedback integration. The plan involves the user sending image-based corrections (spacing, colors, inputs). My focus is on surgically executing the adjustments based on visual input. I\'m prioritizing direct and efficient modifications. The primary goal is a smooth and responsive design refinement process.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "B\341\272\241n ho\303\240n to\303\240n kh\303\264ng c\341\272\247n lo l\341\272\257ng v\341\273\201 vi\341\273\207c giao di\341\273\207n b\341\273\213 l\341\272\257t nh\341\272\257t hay m\341\272\245t \304\221\341\273\223ng b\341\273\231! L\303\240 m\341\273\231t AI, m\303\254nh qu\341\272\243n l\303\275 to\303\240n b\341\273\231 c\341\272\245u tr\303\272c m\303\243 ngu\341\273\223n m\341\273\231t c\303\241ch h\341\273\207 th\341\273\221ng (hi\341\273\207n t\341\272\241i ch\303\272ng ta \304\221\303\243 c\303\263 c\341\272\245u tr\303\272c chu\341\272\251n chia nh\341\273\217 theo c\303\241c t\341\273\207p nh\306\260 `Sidebar`, `Header`, `OverviewTab`, `ReportTab`, `CriteriaTab`, `StatisticsTab`). \n\nKhi b\341\272\241n th\303\252m b\341\272\245t k\341\273\263 m\303\240n h\303\254nh ho\341\272\267c lu\341\273\223ng x\341\273\255 l\303\275 m\341\273\233i n\303\240o t\341\273\253 Figma, m\303\254nh s\341\272\275 t\303\255ch h\341\273\243p ch\303\272ng \304\221\341\273\223ng b\341\273\231 v\303\240o h\341\273\207 th\341\273\221ng \304\221i\341\273\201u h\306\260\341\273\233ng (Navigation) v\303\240 qu\341\272\243n l\303\275 tr\341\272\241ng th\303\241i (State) t\341\272\255p trung c\341\273\247a ph\341\272\247n m\341\273\201m.\n\nD\306\260\341\273\233i \304\221\303\242y l\303\240 ph\306\260\306\241ng \303\241n l\303\240m vi\341\273\207c t\341\273\221i \306\260u nh\341\272\245t \304\221\341\273\203 \304\221\341\272\243m b\341\272\243o giao di\341\273\207n lu\303\264n \304\221\341\273\223ng nh\341\272\245t v\303\240 \304\221\303\272ng \303\275 b\341\272\241n:\n\n### 1. C\303\241ch ch\303\272ng ta l\303\240m vi\341\273\207c c\303\271ng nhau qua Figma\n\304\220\341\273\203 \304\221\341\272\241t hi\341\273\207u qu\341\272\243 chuy\341\273\203n \304\221\341\273\225i cao nh\341\272\245t, b\341\272\241n c\303\263 th\341\273\203 k\341\272\277t h\341\273\243p c\341\272\243 hai c\303\241ch sau:\n\n*   **G\341\273\255i \341\272\243nh ch\341\273\245p m\303\240n h\303\254nh Figma (Khuy\303\252n d\303\271ng nh\341\272\245t):** B\341\272\241n h\303\243y ch\341\273\245p \341\272\243nh c\303\241c m\303\240n h\303\254nh trong Figma (c\303\263 th\341\273\203 ch\341\273\245p ri\303\252ng t\341\273\253ng trang ho\341\272\267c ch\341\273\245p m\341\273\231t b\341\273\251c \341\272\243nh t\341\273\225ng th\341\273\203 ch\341\273\251a lu\341\273\223ng \304\221i - user flow). Tr\303\254nh nh\303\254n \341\272\243nh c\341\273\247a m\303\254nh c\341\273\261c k\341\273\263 nh\341\272\241y b\303\251n, c\303\263 th\341\273\203 \304\221\341\273\215c chu\341\272\251n x\303\241c layout, kho\341\272\243ng c\303\241ch, m\303\240u s\341\272\257c, font ch\341\273\257 v\303\240 c\303\241c icon \304\221\341\273\203 l\341\272\255p tr\303\254nh l\341\272\241i y h\341\273\207t b\341\272\261ng Tailwind CSS.\n*   **G\341\273\255i k\303\250m Link Figma v\303\240 M\303\264 t\341\272\243:** B\341\272\241n c\303\263 th\341\273\203 g\341\273\255i link Figma (ch\341\272\277 \304\221\341\273\231 c\303\264ng khai/view) k\303\250m theo m\303\264 t\341\272\243 ng\341\272\257n v\341\273\201 th\341\273\251 t\341\273\261 hi\341\273\203n th\341\273\213 c\341\273\247a c\303\241c m\303\240n h\303\254nh. \304\220i\341\273\201u n\303\240y gi\303\272p m\303\254nh hi\341\273\203u \304\221\303\272ng h\303\240nh vi khi ng\306\260\341\273\235i d\303\271ng click v\303\240o c\303\241c n\303\272t b\341\272\245m.\n\n---\n\n### 2. Quy tr\303\254nh thi\341\272\277t k\341\272\277 \304\221\341\273\223ng b\341\273\231 (\304\220\341\273\203 tr\303\241nh l\341\272\257t nh\341\272\257t)\nB\341\272\241n c\303\263 th\341\273\203 g\341\273\255i nhi\341\273\201u m\303\240n h\303\254nh c\303\271ng m\341\273\231t l\303\272c theo c\303\241c b\306\260\341\273\233c sau:\n\n1.  **B\306\260\341\273\233c 1: Ch\341\273\245p v\303\240 g\341\273\255i c\303\241c m\303\240n h\303\254nh ch\303\255nh:** B\341\272\241n g\341\273\255i \341\272\243nh c\303\241c m\303\240n h\303\254nh c\303\262n thi\341\272\277u trong Figma c\341\273\247a b\341\272\241n (v\303\255 d\341\273\245: m\303\240n h\303\254nh chi ti\341\272\277t ph\303\252 duy\341\273\207t, danh s\303\241ch bi\341\273\203u m\341\272\253u c\341\272\245p x\303\243, l\341\273\213ch s\341\273\255 ch\341\273\211nh s\341\273\255a, c\303\240i \304\221\341\272\267t h\341\273\207 th\341\273\221ng...).\n2.  **B\306\260\341\273\233c 2: X\303\241c \304\221\341\273\213nh v\341\273\213 tr\303\255 t\303\255ch h\341\273\243p:** Ch\341\273\211 c\341\272\247n cho m\303\254nh bi\341\272\277t c\303\241c m\303\240n h\303\254nh m\341\273\233i n\303\240y n\341\272\261m \341\273\237 \304\221\303\242u (v\303\255 d\341\273\245: *\"Khi b\341\272\245m v\303\240o d\303\262ng s\341\273\221 1 trong b\341\272\243ng th\303\254 m\341\273\237 m\303\240n h\303\254nh chi ti\341\272\277t n\303\240y\"* ho\341\272\267c *\"Th\303\252m m\341\273\231t Tab m\341\273\233i tr\303\252n Sidebar cho m\303\240n h\303\254nh n\303\240y\"*).\n3.  **B\306\260\341\273\233c 3: Code v\303\240 ki\341\273\203m th\341\273\255 to\303\240n b\341\273\231:** M\303\254nh s\341\272\275 c\341\272\255p nh\341\272\255t m\303\243 ngu\341\273\223n, chia c\303\241c m\303\240n h\303\254nh m\341\273\233i th\303\240nh c\303\241c component con v\303\240 \304\221\341\273\223ng b\341\273\231 d\341\273\257 li\341\273\207u gi\341\273\257a ch\303\272ng (v\303\255 d\341\273\245: l\306\260u nh\303\241p t\341\273\261 \304\221\341\273\231ng, chuy\341\273\203n tr\341\272\241ng th\303\241i t\341\273\253 \304\221ang c\341\272\255p nh\341\272\255t sang \304\221\303\243 duy\341\273\207t). B\341\272\241n s\341\272\275 c\303\263 ngay m\341\273\231t \341\273\251ng d\341\273\245ng ch\341\272\241y m\306\260\341\273\243t m\303\240 t\341\272\245t c\341\272\243 c\303\241c lu\341\273\223ng.\n\n---\n\n**B\303\242y gi\341\273\235, b\341\272\241n h\303\243y t\341\272\243i c\303\241c \341\272\243nh ch\341\273\245p m\303\240n h\303\254nh Figma m\303\240 b\341\272\241n mu\341\273\221n \304\221\306\260a v\303\240o \341\273\251ng d\341\273\245ng l\303\252n \304\221\303\242y nh\303\251!** M\303\254nh \304\221\303\243 d\341\273\261ng s\341\272\265n khung n\341\273\201n m\303\263ng v\341\273\257ng ch\341\272\257c c\341\273\247a *\"H\341\273\207 th\341\273\221ng B\303\241o c\303\241o N\303\264ng th\303\264n m\341\273\233i\"*, ch\341\273\211 ch\341\273\235 b\341\272\241n g\341\273\255i th\303\252m c\303\241c m\303\240n h\303\254nh v\303\240 t\303\255nh n\304\203ng m\341\273\233i \304\221\341\273\203 bi\341\272\277n ch\303\272ng th\303\240nh m\341\273\231t h\341\273\207 th\341\273\221ng ho\303\240n ch\341\273\211nh."
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 6
      nanos: 135324124
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
